        public static double getTotalWeightedCompatibility(java.lang.Iterable<GroundCompatibilityKernel> gks)
        Sums the total weighted compatibility (1 - incompatibility) of an iterable container of GroundCompatibilityKernels. WARNING: This method does not account for GroundCompatibilityKernels that were not grounded because they are trivially satisfied.
        Parameters:

        Returns:

      • getExpectedTotalWeightedIncompatibility

        public static double getExpectedTotalWeightedIncompatibility(java.lang.Iterable<GroundCompatibilityKernel> gks)
        Computes the expected total weighted incompatibility of an iterable container of GroundCompatibilityKernels from independently rounding each RandomVariableAtom to 1.0 or 0.0 with probability equal to its current truth value. WARNING: the result of this function is incorrect if the RandomVariableAtoms are subject to any GroundConstraintKernels.
        Parameters:
        gks - the GroundCompatibilityKernels
        Returns:
        the expected total weighted incompatibility
        See Also:
        GroundCompatibilityKernel.getIncompatibility(), GroundCompatibilityKernel.getWeight()
